at_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After losing the first set and going down 4-2 in the second, the British pair stormed back thanks to a strong net game, pushing the Japanese pair to a tiebreak to win the second set.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1141, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.7819324944729481, \"rank\": 0.27589138360459975, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Probably the way that we were playing to that stage would have not suggested that we were likely to come back.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I certainly, from my side, did not feel like I was playing well,\\\" Murray said.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.080859565810054e-29, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can play much better than that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nishikori and Daniel quickly took the lead in the match tiebreak but the Britons hit back, saving five match points before closing the contest out in a little over two hours.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1563, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.8806079201352804, \"rank\": 0.12231235858229865, \"text\": \"Britons\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re